## Data Needed For The Next Pass

- Listing URLs or CSV export with price, beds, baths, sqft, lot size, year built, garage spaces, taxes, status, and description.
- Listing photos or copied listing text so condition, basement, mechanical, garage, and road-noise clues can be reviewed.
- Routing/amenity providers or local GIS sources for Life Time, Montessori/daycare, parks, trails, and commute estimates.
- Additional public records where available for sale history, permits, flood zone, school-boundary verification, and tax detail.
- Any agent notes, disclosures, seller timing, offer deadline, or inspection reports.

## Recommended Next Action

Keep these homes as **diligence-ranked candidates**. Do not tour or reject from
this pass alone. Verify listing details, disclosures, commute timing,
Montessori/daycare availability, and material public-record flags before making
tour or offer decisions.
